Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.19,0:01:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,这正是忍者联军之术
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.34,0:01:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可悲了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们怀揣的希望根本就不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:02:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今 他们也将一并不复存在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十尾差不多该出动了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第五杜门 开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次不是针对十尾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是针对我们发动的攻击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是 擒贼先擒王是基本常识
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.35,0:02:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把控制十尾的他俩干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是想得手的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须先阻止十尾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.23,0:02:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十尾不是被封住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.29,0:02:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩部的骨头脱臼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 感知水球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直堪比小行星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思议…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.51,0:03:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十尾方才并非我们所阻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是为了变身蓄力才一动不动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样才能阻止这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去 根本奈何不了他俩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此也要阻止它 否则我们就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓尿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其害怕 还不如积蓄些查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以便随时配合总部下达的指令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须先封锁十尾的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则无法攻击控制它的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是怎么才能封锁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我族最擅长的束缚敌人的术
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用在那种庞然大物上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便消耗再多的查克拉 效果也微乎其微
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亥一 快联络卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据你刚刚汇报的一系列情报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想确认一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十尾越来越难控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用柱间的细胞加强束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种状态下的十尾究竟拥有多大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你难道不想确认一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会告诉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何为绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿角先生 暂且中断一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.46,0:04:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿角大人 亥一大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 神威根本来不及
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用土遁抬高它的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然可以攻击这么远
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和之前的尾兽根本不是一个等级
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威力太惊人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才射了一发就开始摇晃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来控制得还不够好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续发射
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么远的城镇 一瞬间就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才起就很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它似乎专门攻击远处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 所有的城镇和人都在射程范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:05:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在避难的大名以及留守村子的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有各国的普通居民都有危险了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战场上的忍者们 正是为了保护他们而战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它想断了我们的信念吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个方向…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.46,0:06:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 青大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请冷静听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿角 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好本职工作即可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最后的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联络战场上的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想到了阻止十尾的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来 联军的指挥部就摧毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本常识而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻正在战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用说多余的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井野也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要按照父亲所说的去做就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是作战胜利的关键
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿角大叔和亥一大叔他们到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁次 你向右回旋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八卦掌回天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别发呆 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是战场 现在正在战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难免有人员伤亡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 作战计划失败的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都会死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿丸和井野的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会说“逝于子前乃忍者所愿”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:09:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如我的父亲一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 你的力量在作战中不可或缺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了战斗的顺利 无论如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都要保护鸣人君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住 日向乃木叶最强一族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本想在他们大言不惭之前发动攻击的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但十尾不是很好控制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前这个形态还能支撑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不成为人柱力就无法控制十尾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让我成为十尾的人柱力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这具秽土转生的尸身可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须是有生命的血肉之躯才可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.84,0:09:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秽土转生的你就喜欢拉人同归于尽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却没不惜自爆地用尾兽球攻击脚下的联军
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:10:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你怕我也成为炮灰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的顾虑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了成为人柱力 必须真正复活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就需要我舍身对你施展轮回天生术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在正处在不得不对我言听计从的微妙立场上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当年的小兔崽子 翅膀也变硬了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打从一开始 我就没当你是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后的一切就由你决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要让他们彻底知道何谓绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木遁.扦插之术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在九尾的力量恢复之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我的山土术应该可以抵挡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 凝聚查克拉需要时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太多了 回天应付不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了 宁次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功变成仙人模式了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能光依靠你这个天才
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螺旋手里剑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.36,0:11:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八卦空壁掌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 被瞄准了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅靠雏田和宁次的空掌…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土遁.山土之术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医疗班
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪儿 这里有重伤者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏田大小姐可以为你而牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 你的命…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止一条
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来 我的命…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也成为其中之一了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么能死在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是对日向一族…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我依然记得你把曾经的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从命运的诅咒中解救出来的那番话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…为了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜失去生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,称我为天才
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我不一样 不是拖后腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲大人 我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您为了保护同伴而选择死亡的那种自由感受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说“绝不会让同伴受到伤害”吗 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会让同伴受到伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的那句“绝不会让同伴受到伤害”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 看看四周 再说一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:15:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有种再说一次试试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,触摸同伴逐渐冰冷的身躯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切实地感受一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁次…死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日差 对不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁次他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来这种事还会继续
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那幼稚的话语和理念都会变为虚无
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是空谈理想和希望的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 这种现实还值得留恋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲和母亲不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父自来也也不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 只要你继续和我对立
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.85,0:15:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴将会一个接一个逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界不会再有认可你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:15:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带土
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后等待你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你最熟悉 最恐怖的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直和原来的我如出一辙呢 带土
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人过不了多久就会崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想摧毁联军的核心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何必存在于这种现实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该过来了吧 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才宁次哥哥的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“鸣人的命不止一条”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不会让同伴受到伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的话和你的信念都不是虚无啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁次哥哥记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并诠释了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止是鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.07,0:17:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将这番话语和信念牢记于心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互相支撑并连接着彼此的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为这样才是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果大家舍弃了这番话语和信念
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁次哥哥所做的一切就毫无意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是真的杀害自己的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斩断和同伴的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.79,0:17:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:18:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我们一起站起来吧 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,言出必行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是我的忍道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 雏田大小姐可以为你而牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 你的命…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…不止一条
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘了老夫也在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会斩断羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不会舍弃同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可实际上 宁次…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.23,0:18:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再继续啰嗦试试
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信不信我打爆你 然后占据你的身体 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你难道忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父母在你刚出生不久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也做过和宁次相同的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不惜牺牲自己 将作为敌人的老夫封印在你的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并把未来托付于你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:19:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的命打一出生 就已经和那两条命紧密相连了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不采取任何行动 非要等鸣人的反应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你十分在意鸣人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别急
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么干不仅十尾会受伤 连你也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十尾的表皮很坚韧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎瞄准了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充电完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请小心 蜂大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃我一招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜂大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万万不要乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无需担心 守护联军 由我操心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.03,0:20:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是爸爸和妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在为止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的命早就不止一条了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.94,0:20:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏田 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏有你在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有宁次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人的手 宽大有力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.92,0:21:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.22,0:21:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们上吧 雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.31,0:21:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人非常安心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.57,0:22:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,一路走来 很多同伴我都无力保护
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.42,0:22:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,在牢笼里只能等死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.34,0:22:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,真是绝佳的暗喻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.93,0:23:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,你们就像刚才那个枉死的小鬼一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.44,0:23:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,宁次的意志永不泯灭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.77,0:23:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,下集 火影忍者疾风传
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,忍耐并活跃着的人们
